        "content": "<p>One weird thing is that when you create new streams, sometimes it won't \"subscribe\" everyone to it.</p>",
        "id": 191511827,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986102
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/21317/jeo1Ud4Iax2iZl5HyHt4nGpV/image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/21317/jeo1Ud4Iax2iZl5HyHt4nGpV/image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/21317/jeo1Ud4Iax2iZl5HyHt4nGpV/image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 191511873,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986120
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>That might be a feature and not a bug</p>",
        "id": 191511926,
        "sender_full_name": "Jules Hedges",
        "timestamp": 1584986148
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you look at this screenshot, on the right, the people who's names are darker are not subscribed to the stream I'm currently in.</p>",
        "id": 191511942,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986152
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's definitely a feature.</p>",
        "id": 191512001,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986164
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But I mean the default is to not add people to it.</p>",
        "id": 191512025,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986175
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I've seen instances where someone creates a new stream and then starts talking to themselves, and then wonders why nobody is responding.</p>",
        "id": 191512096,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986211
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>One benefit of the subscription thing is that we can create a \"memes\" stream. Then whoever is \"no nonsense\" can simply not subscribe to it.</p>",
        "id": 191512422,
        "sender_full_name": "Joe Moeller",
        "timestamp": 1584986329
    }
